  "page": "Humfrey Wagstaff",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wagstaff\" title=\"House Wagstaff\"><img alt=\"House Wagstaff.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_Wagstaff.svg/50px-House_Wagstaff.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_Wagstaff.svg/75px-House_Wagstaff.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/House_Wagstaff.svg/100px-House_Wagstaff.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Humfrey Wagstaff</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wagstaff\" title=\"House Wagstaff\"><img alt=\"House Wagstaff.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_Wagstaff.svg/50px-House_Wagstaff.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_Wagstaff.svg/75px-House_Wagstaff.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/House_Wagstaff.svg/100px-House_Wagstaff.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Humfrey_Wagstaff_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Humfrey Wagstaff by Lopata 4.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/Humfrey_Wagstaff_by_Lopata_4.jpg/350px-Humfrey_Wagstaff_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/Humfrey_Wagstaff_by_Lopata_4.jpg/525px-Humfrey_Wagstaff_by_Lopata_4.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1b/Humfrey_Wagstaff_by_Lopata_4.jpg/700px-Humfrey_Wagstaff_by_Lopata_4.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Humfrey by Lopata 4</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">Castellan</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Grandview\" title=\"Grandview\">Grandview</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wagstaff\" title=\"House Wagstaff\">House Wagstaff</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Grandison\" title=\"House Grandison\">House Grandison</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stormlander\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_230_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">230</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_232_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">232&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Humfrey Wagstaff</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wagstaff\" title=\"House Wagstaff\">House Wagstaff</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Grandview\" title=\"Grandview\">Grandview</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/House_Grandison\" title=\"House Grandison\">House Grandison</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Wagstaff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Humfrey had a spotted head and <a href=\"/index.php/Hawk\" title=\"Hawk\">hawk</a> nose. He was a proud man.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Wagstaff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When he was sixty-five, Humfrey was betrothed to a sixteen-year-old <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_Tarth\" title=\"Brienne Tarth\">Brienne Tarth</a>, her third and final match. On the day of their <a href=\"/index.php/Betrothal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Betrothal\">betrothal</a>, Humfrey told Brienne that he would expect her to wear only women's clothes after they <a href=\"/index.php/Married\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Married\">married</a>, warning her that he would chastise her if she would not obey him. Brienne, however, told Humfrey that she would accept punishment only from a man who could beat her in a fight. The <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> turned purple with anger, yet agreed to put on his armor and fight her to teach her a woman's proper place. They fought with blunted weapons, with Brienne wielding a spike-less mace. The girl broke Humfrey's collarbone and two ribs, causing the betrothal to be called off.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Wagstaff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Her hand went to her sword hilt, and she found herself wondering if Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Shadrich\" title=\"Shadrich\">Shadrich</a> would think her easy prey just because she was a woman. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Grandison\" title=\"House Grandison\">Grandison's</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> had once made that error. Humfrey Wagstaff was his name; a proud old man of five-and-sixty, with a nose like a <a href=\"/index.php/Hawk\" title=\"Hawk\">hawk</a> and a spotted head.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_Tarth\" title=\"Brienne Tarth\">Brienne Tarth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Wagstaff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued)#Humfrey_Wagstaff\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued)\">Humfrey Wagstaff</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 9\">Chapter 9</a>, Brienne II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNe